mixin InvitePeople(config)
  - var config = Object.assign({ inputFieldColumn: 'col-md-7', buttonColumn: 'col-lg-4' }, config);
  .card&attributes(attributes)
    .card-body.text-center.py-5
      .row.justify-content-center
        .col-7.col-md-5
          img.img-fluid(src=`${CWD}assets/img/icons/spot-illustrations/41.png`, alt="" style='width:58%;')
      h3.mt-3.fw-normal.fs-2(class=config.titleClass) Invite a friend, you both get $100
      p.lead.mb-5 Invite your friends and start working together in seconds. 
        if(config.brClass)
          br(class=config.brClass)
        | Everyone you invite will receive a welcome email.

      .row.justify-content-center
        div(class=config.inputFieldColumn)
          form.row.gx-2
            .col-sm.mb-2.mb-sm-0
              input.form-control(type='email' placeholder="Email address" aria-label="Recipient's username")
            .col-sm-auto
              button.btn.btn-primary.d-block.w-100(type="submit") Send Invitation

    .card-footer.bg-light.text-center.pt-4
      .row.justify-content-center
        .col-11.col-sm-10
          h4.fw-normal.mb-0.fs-1(class=config.footerTitleClass) More ways to 
            br.d-sm-none 
            |  invite your friends
          .row.gx-2.my-4
            div(class=config.buttonColumn)
              button.btn.btn-falcon-default.d-block.w-100.mb-2(class=config.buttonClass)
                img(src=`${CWD}assets/img/logos/gmail.png`, width="20" alt="")
                span.fw-medium.ms-2 Invite from Gmail
            div(class=config.buttonColumn)
              button.btn.btn-falcon-default.d-block.w-100.mb-2(data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#copyLinkModal" class=config.buttonClass)
                span.fas.fa-link.text-700
                span.fw-medium.ms-2 Copy Link

              #copyLinkModal.modal.fade(tabindex='-1' role='dialog' aria-labelledby='copyLinkModalLabel' aria-hidden='true')
                .modal-dialog(role='document')
                  .modal-content.overflow-hidden
                    .modal-header
                      h5#copyLinkModalLabel.modal-title Your personal referral link
                      button.btn-close(type='button' data-bs-dismiss='modal' aria-label='Close')
                    .modal-body.bg-light.p-4
                      form
                        input.form-control.form-control-sm.invitation-link(value="https://falcon.com/invited")

            div(class=config.buttonColumn)
              button.btn.btn-falcon-default.d-block.w-100.ms-0(class=config.buttonClass)
                span.fab.fa-facebook-square.text-facebook(data-fa-transform="grow-2")
                span.fw-medium.ms-2 Share on Facebook
          p.mb-2.fs--1 Once youâ€™ve invited friends, you can 
            a(href="#!") view the status of your referrals
            br.d-none.d-lg-block.d-xxl-none
            |  or visit our 
            a(href="#!") Help Center 
            | if you have any questions.  